# ✅ FINAL FIX (you must recreate subscriptions)

Now create **clean subscriptions pointing to v4.20 catalog**

---

## 📌 Apply this YAML

```yaml
apiVersion: operators.coreos.com/v1alpha1
kind: Subscription
metadata:
  name: ocs-operator
  namespace: openshift-storage
spec:
  channel: stable-4.20
  name: ocs-operator
  source: cs-redhat-operator-index-v4-20
  sourceNamespace: openshift-marketplace
---
apiVersion: operators.coreos.com/v1alpha1
kind: Subscription
metadata:
  name: mcg-operator
  namespace: openshift-storage
spec:
  channel: stable-4.20
  name: mcg-operator
  source: cs-redhat-operator-index-v4-20
  sourceNamespace: openshift-marketplace
---
apiVersion: operators.coreos.com/v1alpha1
