# 🧠 Important lesson (very key)

In disconnected OCP:

👉 ODF = **multi-operator stack**

| Component    | Needed          |
| ------------ | --------------- |
| odf-operator | orchestration   |
| ocs-operator | core            |
| rook-ceph    | storage         |
| mcg          | object (NooBaa) |
| cephcsi      | CSI             |

👉 If ANY missing → cluster won’t start

